{"Sid":0,"Did":25470,"Id":"312297","Title":"劉文榮訪談錄","ImageUrl":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/collection/2020-01-04/a062430f-2fd1-4582-a71f-d94f4c1e6172/p1.51-DSC_0375劉文榮.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/collection/2020-01-04/92ac3ed9-dac5-45b0-864a-de1fed1199f4/p1.51-DSC_0376劉文榮.jpg","IndexCode":"Culture_Object","CustomColumns":{"Description":"\n\n劉文榮，民國17年5月24日出生，河北省保定市；丈夫為趙文英，已殁，民國11年2月19日出生，河北省清苑縣趙庄村，官拜陸軍上校，曾在8兵團68軍81師任職。18歲的時候嫁給丈夫。\n\n民國38年大逃難時，帶著兒子離開故鄉，當時丈夫在廣州擔任部隊營長，無法與眷屬一同搭船撤退，險些妻離子散，受訪者的婆婆亦於逃難的過程中在海上身故。抵臺灣後被安排搭車先行抵達桃園，在中壢平鎮克難住上3個月後，在由丈夫接到高雄住。\n\n劉文榮的訪談錄清楚記載1949年從中國逃難至臺灣安定的過程，頗值得參考。\n\n","Keyword_Rights_2":"CC BY / CC BY","Keyword_Des_Rights_2":"CC0","Keyword_Longitude":"NULL","Keyword_Latitude":"NULL","Original_Url":"https://cmsdb.culture.tw/object/5CC86C92-F3D2-4DA7-9E09-75D1EF6EF958","Original_Identifier":"312297","Keyword_Subject_1":"社會與政治","alias":"","alternativeHeadline":"","Keywords":"國軍撤退 / 陸軍步兵學校 / 黃埔新村","dates":"採訪時間 / 民國/戰後時期","LastUpdateTime":"2020/01/04 16:48:14","Creator":"顧超光、莊榮華","publisher":"","mediaType":"文件","language":"","timelines":"戰後時期 (1945~)","city":"高雄市鳳山區","address":"","lng":"","lat":"","contributors":"","contributor":"顧超光、張岳茹","size":"","admin":"","award":"","character":"","contentLocation":"","acquireWay":"","acquireSource":"","storage":"","version":"","isbn":"","onlineAuthLink":"","stuff":"","url":"","createOrgName":"高雄市政府文化局","citation":"","Keyword_Rights_1":"","AllImages":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/collectionOpen/2020-01-04/60a00279-bb4f-4e77-8fce-245b32be83a9/p1.51-DSC_0375劉文榮.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/collectionOpen/2020-01-04/4e0ce532-ca75-45be-87e4-c257a9029538/p1.51-DSC_0376劉文榮.jpg"}}